title: The Official Website of New York State
text: Popular Services Featured Programs File Your Tax Returns for Free Through Free File, eligible New York residents can access no-cost e-filing for federal and New York State tax returns. Encouraging kids & families to put down their electronic devices, enjoy the outdoors, and put their mental & physical health first.
